{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":306,"text":"Hi. My name is Cameron Russell,"},{"time":2950,"text":"and for the last little while,\nI've been a model."},{"time":9003,"text":"Actually, for 10 years."},{"time":12990,"text":"And I feel like"},{"time":15170,"text":"there's an uncomfortable tension\nin the room right now"},{"time":17994,"text":"because I should not have worn this dress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20041,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":21823,"text":"So luckily, I brought an outfit change."},{"time":24321,"text":"This is the first outfit change\non the TED stage,"},{"time":27970,"text":"so you guys are pretty lucky\nto witness it, I think."},{"time":31016,"text":"If some of the women were\nreally horrified when I came out,"},{"time":33957,"text":"you don't have to tell me now,\nbut I'll find out later on Twitter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37124,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":42315,"text":"I'd also note that I'm quite privileged"},{"time":44197,"text":"to be able to transform\nwhat you think of me"},{"time":47275,"text":"in a very brief 10 seconds."},{"time":49938,"text":"Not everybody gets to do that."},{"time":53400,"text":"These heels are very uncomfortable,\nso good thing I wasn't going to wear them."},{"time":59239,"text":"The worst part is putting\nthis sweater over my head,"},{"time":61784,"text":"because that's when\nyou'll all laugh at me,"},{"time":63857,"text":"so don't do anything\nwhile it's over my head."},{"time":67745,"text":"All right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70983,"text":"So, why did I do that?"},{"time":73714,"text":"That was awkward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74944,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76896,"text":"Well --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78031,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":80421,"text":"Hopefully not as awkward as that picture."},{"time":85306,"text":"Image is powerful,"},{"time":88088,"text":"but also, image is superficial."},{"time":93036,"text":"I just totally transformed\nwhat you thought of me, in six seconds."},{"time":97479,"text":"And in this picture,"},{"time":99318,"text":"I had actually never had\na boyfriend in real life."},{"time":102643,"text":"I was totally uncomfortable,"},{"time":104460,"text":"and the photographer\nwas telling me to arch my back"},{"time":106962,"text":"and put my hand in that guy's hair."},{"time":111013,"text":"And of course, barring surgery,"},{"time":113013,"text":"or the fake tan that I got\ntwo days ago for work,"},{"time":116454,"text":"there's very little that we can do\nto transform how we look,"},{"time":120215,"text":"and how we look, though it is\nsuperficial and immutable,"},{"time":123671,"text":"has a huge impact on our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128034,"text":"So today, for me, being\nfearless means being honest."},{"time":132662,"text":"And I am on this stage\nbecause I am a model."},{"time":135547,"text":"I am on this stage because\nI am a pretty, white woman,"},{"time":139274,"text":"and in my industry,\nwe call that a sexy girl."},{"time":142039,"text":"I'm going to answer the questions\nthat people always ask me,"},{"time":144910,"text":"but with an honest twist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146232,"text":"So the first question is,\nhow do you become a model?"},{"time":149134,"text":"I always just say, \"Oh, I was scouted,\""},{"time":151167,"text":"but that means nothing."},{"time":152349,"text":"The real way that I became a model"},{"time":155454,"text":"is I won a genetic lottery,\nand I am the recipient of a legacy,"},{"time":158941,"text":"and maybe you're wondering\nwhat is a legacy."},{"time":161061,"text":"Well, for the past few centuries"},{"time":163807,"text":"we have defined beauty\nnot just as health and youth"},{"time":169325,"text":"and symmetry that we're biologically\nprogrammed to admire,"},{"time":173111,"text":"but also as tall, slender figures,"},{"time":176647,"text":"and femininity and white skin."},{"time":179894,"text":"And this is a legacy\nthat was built for me,"},{"time":181966,"text":"and it's a legacy\nthat I've been cashing out on."},{"time":184440,"text":"And I know there are\npeople in the audience"},{"time":186494,"text":"who are skeptical at this point,"},{"time":188210,"text":"and maybe there are\nsome fashionistas who are like,"},{"time":190711,"text":"\"Wait. Naomi. Tyra. Joan Smalls. Liu Wen.\""},{"time":193254,"text":"And first, I commend you on your model\nknowledge. Very impressive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196421,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":198077,"text":"But unfortunately,\nI have to inform you that in 2007,"},{"time":201630,"text":"a very inspired NYU Ph.D. student"},{"time":204140,"text":"counted all the models on the runway,\nevery single one that was hired,"},{"time":207766,"text":"and of the 677 models that were hired,"},{"time":210894,"text":"only 27, or less than four percent,\nwere non-white."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215637,"text":"The next question people always ask is,"},{"time":217594,"text":"\"Can I be a model when I grow up?\""},{"time":219243,"text":"And the first answer is, \"I don't know,\nthey don't put me in charge of that.\""},{"time":222901,"text":"But the second answer,"},{"time":224318,"text":"and what I really want to say\nto these little girls is,"},{"time":227096,"text":"\"Why? You know? You can be anything."},{"time":229110,"text":"You could be the President\nof the United States,"},{"time":231380,"text":"or the inventor of the next Internet,"},{"time":233181,"text":"or a ninja cardiothoracic surgeon poet,"},{"time":235163,"text":"which would be awesome,\nbecause you'd be the first one.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":237854,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":240040,"text":"If, after this amazing list,\nthey still are like,"},{"time":242398,"text":"\"No, no, Cameron, I want to be a model,\""},{"time":244327,"text":"well, then I say, \"Be my boss.\""},{"time":245965,"text":"Because I'm not in charge of anything,"},{"time":247855,"text":"and you could be the editor in chief\nof American Vogue"},{"time":250406,"text":"or the CEO of H&amp;M,\nor the next Steven Meisel."},{"time":253031,"text":"Saying that you want to be\na model when you grow up"},{"time":255436,"text":"is akin to saying that you want to win\nthe Powerball when you grow up."},{"time":258794,"text":"It's out of your control,\nand it's awesome,"},{"time":262238,"text":"and it's not a career path."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264316,"text":"I will demonstrate for you now\n10 years of accumulated model knowledge,"},{"time":268307,"text":"because unlike cardiothoracic surgeons,"},{"time":270236,"text":"it can just be distilled right now."},{"time":272962,"text":"So, if the photographer is right there,"},{"time":276046,"text":"the light is right there, like a nice HMI,"},{"time":278127,"text":"and the client says,\n\"We want a walking shot,\""},{"time":280298,"text":"this leg goes first, nice and long,\nthis arm goes back, this arm goes forward,"},{"time":284006,"text":"the head is at three quarters,\nand you just go back and forth,"},{"time":286948,"text":"just do that, and then you look back\nat your imaginary friends,"},{"time":289972,"text":"300, 400, 500 times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291715,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":293419,"text":"It will look something like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295230,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":297441,"text":"Hopefully less awkward\nthan that one in the middle."},{"time":300393,"text":"That was -- I don't know\nwhat happened there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302968,"text":"Unfortunately,\nafter you've gone to school,"},{"time":305099,"text":"and you have a résumé\nand you've done a few jobs,"},{"time":307453,"text":"you can't say anything anymore,"},{"time":308969,"text":"so if you say you want to be\nthe President of the United States,"},{"time":312040,"text":"but your résumé reads,\n\"Underwear Model: 10 years,\""},{"time":314470,"text":"people give you a funny look."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315900,"text":"The next question is,\n\"Do they retouch all the photos?\""},{"time":318512,"text":"And yeah, they pretty much\nretouch all the photos,"},{"time":320917,"text":"but that is only a small component\nof what's happening."},{"time":324006,"text":"This picture is the very first\npicture that I ever took,"},{"time":326748,"text":"and it's also the very first time\nthat I had worn a bikini,"},{"time":329581,"text":"and I didn't even have my period yet."},{"time":331385,"text":"I know we're getting personal,\nbut I was a young girl."},{"time":334536,"text":"This is what I looked like with my grandma\njust a few months earlier."},{"time":339016,"text":"Here's me on the same day as this shoot."},{"time":341216,"text":"My friend got to come."},{"time":342584,"text":"Here's me at a slumber party\na few days before I shot French Vogue."},{"time":346679,"text":"Here's me on the soccer team\nand in V Magazine."},{"time":350787,"text":"And here's me today."},{"time":352247,"text":"And I hope what you're seeing"},{"time":354307,"text":"is that these pictures\nare not pictures of me."},{"time":356505,"text":"They are constructions,"},{"time":357943,"text":"and they are constructions\nby a group of professionals,"},{"time":360871,"text":"by hairstylists and makeup artists\nand photographers and stylists"},{"time":363991,"text":"and all of their assistants\nand pre-production and post-production,"},{"time":367207,"text":"and they build this."},{"time":368239,"text":"That's not me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369333,"text":"Okay, so the next question\npeople always ask me is,"},{"time":371754,"text":"\"Do you get free stuff?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":373104,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":374174,"text":"I do have too many 8-inch heels\nwhich I never get to wear,"},{"time":377445,"text":"except for earlier,"},{"time":379064,"text":"but the free stuff that I get\nis the free stuff that I get in real life,"},{"time":382549,"text":"and that's what we don't like\nto talk about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384803,"text":"I grew up in Cambridge,"},{"time":386094,"text":"and one time I went into a store\nand I forgot my money"},{"time":388690,"text":"and they gave me the dress for free."},{"time":390822,"text":"When I was a teenager,\nI was driving with my friend"},{"time":393342,"text":"who was an awful driver\nand she ran a red and of course,"},{"time":396033,"text":"we got pulled over,"},{"time":397246,"text":"and all it took was a \"Sorry, officer,\"\nand we were on our way."},{"time":402363,"text":"And I got these free things\nbecause of how I look,"},{"time":405569,"text":"not who I am, and there are\npeople paying a cost"},{"time":408388,"text":"for how they look and not who they are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410630,"text":"I live in New York, and last year,"},{"time":412274,"text":"of the 140,000 teenagers\nthat were stopped and frisked,"},{"time":416077,"text":"86% of them were black and Latino,\nand most of them were young men."},{"time":420116,"text":"And there are only 177,000\nyoung black and Latino men in New York,"},{"time":424602,"text":"so for them, it's not a question\nof, \"Will I get stopped?\""},{"time":427341,"text":"but \"How many times will I get stopped?\nWhen will I get stopped?\""},{"time":430423,"text":"When I was researching this talk,"},{"time":432019,"text":"I found out that of the 13-year-old girls\nin the United States,"},{"time":435198,"text":"53% don't like their bodies,"},{"time":437885,"text":"and that number goes to 78%\nby the time that they're 17."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441981,"text":"So, the last question people ask me is,"},{"time":444903,"text":"\"What is it like to be a model?\""},{"time":446527,"text":"And I think the answer\nthat they're looking for is,"},{"time":448934,"text":"\"If you are a little bit skinnier\nand you have shinier hair,"},{"time":451878,"text":"you will be so happy and fabulous.\""},{"time":454675,"text":"And when we're backstage,"},{"time":456234,"text":"we give an answer\nthat maybe makes it seem like that."},{"time":458781,"text":"We say, \"It's really amazing to travel,\nand it's amazing to get to work"},{"time":462285,"text":"with creative, inspired,\npassionate people.\""},{"time":464909,"text":"And those things are true,\nbut they're only one half of the story,"},{"time":468076,"text":"because the thing\nthat we never say on camera,"},{"time":470678,"text":"that I have never said on camera, is,"},{"time":472774,"text":"\"I am insecure.\""},{"time":475158,"text":"And I'm insecure because I have to think\nabout what I look like every day."},{"time":480600,"text":"And if you ever are wondering,"},{"time":483596,"text":"\"If I have thinner thighs\nand shinier hair, will I be happier?\""},{"time":487550,"text":"you just need to meet a group of models,"},{"time":489479,"text":"because they have the thinnest thighs,\nthe shiniest hair and the coolest clothes,"},{"time":493429,"text":"and they're the most physically\ninsecure women probably on the planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496896,"text":"When I was writing this talk,"},{"time":498302,"text":"I found it very difficult\nto strike an honest balance,"},{"time":501295,"text":"because on the one hand,"},{"time":502753,"text":"I felt very uncomfortable\nto come out here and say,"},{"time":505189,"text":"\"Look I've received all these benefits\nfrom a deck stacked in my favor,\""},{"time":508808,"text":"and it also felt really uncomfortable\nto follow that up with,"},{"time":512023,"text":"\"and it doesn't always make me happy.\""},{"time":514411,"text":"But mostly it was difficult to unpack\na legacy of gender and racial oppression"},{"time":520310,"text":"when I am one\nof the biggest beneficiaries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523822,"text":"But I'm also happy\nand honored to be up here"},{"time":526303,"text":"and I think that it's great\nthat I got to come"},{"time":529539,"text":"before 10 or 20 or 30 years had passed\nand I'd had more agency in my career,"},{"time":533236,"text":"because maybe then I wouldn't tell\nthe story of how I got my first job,"},{"time":536734,"text":"or maybe I wouldn't tell the story\nof how I paid for college,"},{"time":539631,"text":"which seems so important right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":542074,"text":"If there's a takeaway to this talk,"},{"time":543996,"text":"I hope it's that we all feel\nmore comfortable acknowledging"},{"time":547623,"text":"the power of image\nin our perceived successes"},{"time":551590,"text":"and our perceived failures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553490,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554866,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}